    - ticket info is shown in the hand
  - when a ticket is moved
    - request: /tickets/move? id, x, y
  - when ticket title is cliced
    - show ticket form
    - when ok is clicked
      - show new title in the hand
      - show new title in the field
      - request: /tickets/rename? id, new
