    - ask really delete the ticket
    - when Y is clicked
      - remove the ticket from the field
      - clear the hand
      - request: /tickets/delete? id
    - when N is clicked
      - do not remove the ticket from the field
      - keep the hand
      - no request

- refactor scheme code (use hashtable as object)

